item.title: Rationale : 2020 Trap Mega-Collaboration
item.dc:creator: INDIR3CT
item.description:
Hello everyone! I am so excited and proud to finally get to share this mega collab! It was so nice being able to work with and learn from some absolutely amazing artists!

Here is the roster of artists in the collaboration… In order…
@Twizard - https://soundcloud.com/twizard-official
@Deru - https://soundcloud.com/derumusic
@The_Osprey - https://soundcloud.com/devyn-fidel
@CLOME - https://soundcloud.com/clomemusic
@Aqzi - https://soundcloud.com/aquax
@Stardust - https://soundcloud.com/isaac-legate
@EVERANGE - https://soundcloud.com/user-401598186
Please please PLEASE… go check out these wonderful artists!

We had a really nice structure to our collaboration, I got to create an intro and an outro, then turn everything inside the track over to the other artists… and I feel we really created something spectacular.

Please give it a listen… and let’s us know what you think.

https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/rationale

Much love,
INDIR3CT
